sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/Dashboard
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant NotebookCtrl as Notebook Controller<br/>Watch & Reconcile
    participant Kubelet as Kubelet<br/>10250/TCP HTTPS mTLS
    participant NotebookPod as Notebook Pod<br/>8888/TCP HTTP
    participant CullingCtrl as Culling Controller<br/>Idle Detection
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>Metrics Scraper

    Note over User,NotebookPod: Flow 1: Notebook Creation
    User->>K8sAPI: POST Notebook CR<br/>HTTPS/6443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>User Auth
    K8sAPI->>NotebookCtrl: Watch Event<br/>Notebook Created<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    NotebookCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create StatefulSet & Service<br/>HTTPS/6443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI->>Kubelet: Schedule Pod<br/>HTTPS/10250<br/>mTLS
    Kubelet-->>NotebookPod: Start Jupyter Server
    NotebookPod-->>NotebookCtrl: Pod Ready
    NotebookCtrl->>K8sAPI: Update Notebook Status<br/>HTTPS/6443<br/>ServiceAccount Token

    Note over CullingCtrl,NotebookPod: Flow 2: Notebook Culling (Idle Detection)
    CullingCtrl->>NotebookPod: GET /api/kernels<br/>HTTP/8888<br/>No Auth
    NotebookPod-->>CullingCtrl: Kernel Activity JSON<br/>last_activity timestamp
    CullingCtrl->>CullingCtrl: Check if idle > CULL_IDLE_TIME
    CullingCtrl->>K8sAPI: Add kubeflow-resource-stopped annotation<br/>HTTPS/6443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI->>NotebookCtrl: Watch Event<br/>Annotation Changed
    NotebookCtrl->>K8sAPI: Scale StatefulSet to 0<br/>HTTPS/6443<br/>ServiceAccount Token

    Note over Prometheus,NotebookCtrl: Flow 3: Metrics Collection
    Prometheus->>NotebookCtrl: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP/8080<br/>No Auth
    NotebookCtrl-->>Prometheus: Prometheus Metrics<br/>notebook_creation_total<br/>notebook_culling_total
